---
title: Double Kiwi-Spiced Chicken & Roast Veggie Toss with Hollandaise & Almonds
description: Zest it up, tonight's chicken is getting a hearty coating of our new Kiwi tastetastic spice blend, bursting with specially crafted flavours we know you'll love. Roast the veggies in a zesty and peppery seasoning to give them a delicious kick.

